org.relationlearn.classifiers - package org.relationlearn.classifiers
Provides facilities for classifier training, storage and classification of Instance objects.
org.relationlearn.exception - package org.relationlearn.exception
Provides exception wrappers to ease user in error cause detection.
org.relationlearn.filters - package org.relationlearn.filters
Provides facilities to create text filters and generate weka compatible Instance objects with them.
org.relationlearn.model - package org.relationlearn.model
Provides facilites for in-memory representation of the input data obtained with any of the InputParser possible implementations.
org.relationlearn.util - package org.relationlearn.util
Provides utility methods, classes and enumerators for common tasks performed by other package classes.
org.relationlearn.util.io - package org.relationlearn.util.io
Provides facilites for the parsing of input data and the generation of output data in multiple formats.
OutputGenerator - Interface in org.relationlearn.util.io
The OutputGenerator interface defines the rules any implementationg should follow in order to provide output format for representing the data in a Map of RelationDigraph objects.
